template<class F> packaged_task(F) -> packaged_task<see below>;




-?- Constraints: &F::operator() is well-formed when treated as an unevaluated operand 
and decltype(&F::operator()) is of the form R(G::*)(A...) cv &opt 
noexceptopt for a class type G.


-?- Remarks: The deduced type is packaged_task<R(A...)>.


